        "zType": "TEXT_EVENTSTORY_PLAYER_TRUCE_HOSTAGE",
        "English": "An unassuming envoy from {PLAYER-0} enters the court, head bowed courteously. He states that he has been given authority to speak for his nation's leadership.\n\nThe {PLAYER-0,3} will gladly establish a truce and end the fighting, if only we will return their hostage."
