        "English": "Our people have suffered greatly in the ongoing conflict. All the gold we spend on link(DIPLOMACY_WAR) could be spent here in {PLAYER-1}. Perhaps it is time for a link(DIPLOMACY_TRUCE) with {PLAYER-0,0}."
