        "zType": "TEXT_EVENTSTORY_PLAYER_TECH_TRADE",
        "English": "An emissary arrives from our friends in {PLAYER-0}, where word of our scientific advancement has spread. {PLAYER-0,1} scholars offer to teach us what they know of {TECH-2} if we are willing to share our knowledge of {TECH-3}.\n\nHow shall we respond?"
