        "English": "A mission of {PLAYER-0,1} diplomats arrives with {CHARACTER-SHORT-0}'s blessing. They seek advice on how to unite disparate clans under a unifying system. They have heard stories of our link(TECH_MARTIAL_CODE), and they are open to trading valuable items to understand this way of life.\n\nWhat shall we tell them?"
