        "English": "The famous link(TRAIT_COMMANDER_ARCHETYPE), {CHARACTER-0} is furiously planning a campaign against us! At the head of the {PLAYER-0,1} armies, {G0:he:she} will be a formidable foe. Our one chance to avoid war is to pre-empt it with a generous offer of tribute.\n\n{TEXT_EVENTSTORY_WAR_OFFER_CLOSING}"
