        "English": "Our link(COUNCIL_AMBASSADOR), {CHARACTER-SHORT-2}, failed to complete {G2:his:her} mission to establish a trade network with {PLAYER-0}. The {PLAYER-0,3} are not happy with us and will only accept a gift from us instead."
