        "English": "{PLAYER-0,1} merchants, escorted by armed soldiers, arrive in the capital to negotiate a new trade deal.\n\nThe deal? {PLAYER-0} requires a generous gift of {RESOURCE-2}, or they will send their armies to take it by force."
