        "English": "While dining in the company of {CHARACTER-0}, our {CHARACTER-1} gives a toast dripping with innuendo and sarcasm, \"Here's to our true {PLAYER-0, 1} heir!\"\n\n{CHARACTER-0} takes offense and calls for the link(CONCEPT_GENERAL) to be reprimanded."
