        "English": "At twilight, grim-faced and torch-wielding acolytes storm into the court. {CHARACTER-2} marches before them, {G2:his:her} brows furrowed and lips pressed tight.\n\n\"Repent O {G3:King:Queen}! Join us for the dedication of the link(IMPROVEMENT_SHRINE_NUSKA) in {CITY-0}, or face the Nuska's judgment!\""
