        "English": "A group of {TRIBE-1,1} riders thunders through the streets of the capital, headed for the court. {CHARACTER-0} has just learned of our war with the {TRIBE-2} and wishes to supply aid. Apparently, the {TRIBE-1} and the {TRIBE-2} are ancient enemies, and {CHARACTER-SHORT-0} pledges support.\n\nThe leader of the riders offers three options."
