        "English": "{random_R1:You may be interested to learn that:Your courtiers inform you that:A trusted advisor informs you that:Rumor has it that:You have noticed that}, for better or for worse, {CHARACTER-0} is showing signs of taking after {G0:his:her} {G1:father:mother}, {CHARACTER-1}. How this influence will take shape is yet to be seen. \n\nOur nation rejoices at the arrival of another most cunning mind in the court, although one does wonder - on which side shall the coin land?"
